course_description: The third course in a 3-course series prepares the student to implement the DNP project. The full implementation of the project will be addressed, including intervention development, system change, methods of measurement, selection of systems of analysis, and plans for project dissemination.
prerequisites: NRSG 716D or equivalent transfer credit as prerequisite.
